{{Flavour|A devotee of Yredelemnul that has committed to eternal worship and servitude â€” even beyond death.}}

'''Unborn''' are [[Yredelemnul]]-worshiping [[lich]]es whose spell set focuses entirely on powerful [[Necromancy]]. They also possess the ability to [[Injury Mirror|reflect damage]] you inflict upon them back at you. They can be found in [[the Crypt]], [[the Abyss]], and [[the Depths]].

==Spells==
{{Spellcaster5
|number=
|slot1=[[Agony]]
|flags1={{Wizard slot flag}}
